<node CREATED="1493577965595" ID="ID_1914172978" MODIFIED="1493577971467" POSITION="left" TEXT="I have tried a couple"/>
<node CREATED="1493577615097" ID="ID_284408713" MODIFIED="1493577989571" POSITION="left" TEXT="And reached the conclusion that to move forward, we need to attack meaning/content, with all its levels, and remove dualisms. I hope to convince you."/>
